                                                                     ESL Inc. received an $18.2 million Army contract foraircraft electronics.                                                                                                          ECC International Corp. received a $14.2 million Air Forcecontract for maintenance training devices.                                                                                                          Hughes Aircraft Co., a unit of General Motors Corp.,received a $13.9 million Air Force contract for missile raillaunchers.</TEXT></DOC>